"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-29-laura-robson-reveals-andy-murrays-niche-obsession-paris-olympics-21317311\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Andy Murrayis clearly relishing his last ever appearance at anOlympic Gamesand the Team GB star put his retirement plans on hold with a stunning opening-round win in the doubles competition alongsideDan Evanson Sunday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 83, \"end\": 90, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999988891246889, \"rank\": 9.706850572362165e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old announced last week that this summer's Games inPariswould be his swansong showing before he hangs up his racket.\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray had also been expected to compete in the single's tournament, but made the decision to concentrate solely on the men's doubles, and the veteran Britproduced a sensational performance at Roland-Garros to keep his career alive.\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 350, \"end\": 356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.256475781568326e-32, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After saving five match points, Murray and Evans booked their spot in the second round with an epic 2-6, 7-6 (5), 11-9 victory over Japan's Kei Nishikori and Taro Daniel.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.256475781568326e-32, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DaBaby\", \"score\": 0.5464882987138024, \"rank\": 0.8298653462948448, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DaBaby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DaBaby\"}, {\"begin\": 716, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.9986518924472532, \"rank\": 0.0012274742315310084, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Davis_Cup_team\"}, {\"begin\": 724, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kei Nishikori\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\"}, {\"begin\": 742, \"end\": 753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taro Daniel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow\\u00a0Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  Murray later described the incredible comeback win as one of the greatest recoveries of his career.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's probably up there.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pro\\u00adbably the way that we were playing to that stage would have not suggested that we were likely to come back,' the legendary Scot said shortly after the thriller.\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I certainly did not feel like I was playing well.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Evo played well at times but for both of us we can play much better than that.\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then it just all clicked at the end and we played some pretty, pretty good stuff.'\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This summer, Murray is targeting a fourth Olympic medal\\u00a0- but it appears it's not just medals the Scot is chasing in the French capital.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.256475781568326e-32, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking onEurosport, Laura Robson - who won silver alongside Murray at London 2012 - lifted the lid on the two-time Wimbledon champion's niche obsession for collecting Olympic pin badges from other competitors at the Games.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.256475781568326e-32, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1549, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999993191925157, \"rank\": 6.802864971304341e-07, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Wimbledon_Championships\", \"score\": 0.6365048044531387, \"rank\": 0.3169799224121422, \"text\": \"Wimbledon\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Wimbledon_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Wimbledon_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He's taking it very seriously.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He did not do it in 2012 but then followed it up at Rio and Tokyo, he went hard,' Robson explained.\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1787, \"end\": 1790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999918873073, \"rank\": 8.112551981152328e-09, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1795, \"end\": 1800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999789787247548, \"rank\": 2.1020340532565256e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1817, \"end\": 1823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Robson\", \"score\": 0.9999993964745046, \"rank\": 5.815393620895639e-07, \"text\": \"Robson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Robson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Robson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In the athlete's village, he's trying to find the most niche country, the smallest country.'\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Murray might have the \\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u009b\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u00a2\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u00a0\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u00a0\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u009e\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u00ac\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u00ad collection of Olympic pin badges \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098@SportsOrla|@laurarobson5|@andy_murray|#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/9ckxK18MQd  Robson revealed that Murray had managed to track down Romano Puentener, Liechtenstein's sole representative at the Games, for the country's official Olympic pin badge.\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1931, \"end\": 1942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.065049252215183e-49, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2100, \"end\": 2106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Robson\", \"score\": 0.9999993964745046, \"rank\": 5.815393620895639e-07, \"text\": \"Robson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Robson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Robson\"}, {\"begin\": 2121, \"end\": 2127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.256475781568326e-32, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2172, \"end\": 2185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liechtenstein_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9937817455716613, \"rank\": 0.006256861842223384, \"text\": \"Liechtenstein\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liechtenstein_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liechtenstein_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'His one for this week was a guy\\u2026 there is one athlete from Liechtenstein and he was searching the village, high and low, to try and find this poor man,' Robson added.\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2329, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liechtenstein_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9937817455716613, \"rank\": 0.006256861842223384, \"text\": \"Liechtenstein\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liechtenstein_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liechtenstein_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2423, \"end\": 2429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Robson\", \"score\": 0.9999993964745046, \"rank\": 5.815393620895639e-07, \"text\": \"Robson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Robson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Robson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He tracked him down, he's got it, and it was like he had won the Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Honestly, he came in and was showing everyone, \\\"Look what I have got!\\\".\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's a bit unfair in a way because it is a competition and because he's Andy Murray, everyone wants to give him a pin.\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2664, \"end\": 2675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.065049252215183e-49, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's got an unfair [advantage], it's a little unfair!'\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2815, \"enti